item.name: Log In / Create Access Token / Authenticate User

request.description:
Use [base64encode site](https://www.base64encode.org/) to encode your username:password combination and pass in as a header apiKey

** Example below

Username and password combination

`mandeep.s.sidhu@simbaquartz.com:managemyorg@321`

*Encoded string*

`bWFuZGVlcC5zLnNpZGh1QHNpbWJhcXVhcnR6LmNvbTptYW5hZ2VteW9yZ0AzMjE=`
After email confirmation (user clicks on /user/verify) a token is generated which needs to be passed to this API, this API will verify that token and mark the user as verified.
